channel.description: Sorry if I put this in the wrong place, I'm new here. But anyway, I put a new item into my server. I put the INTS into itemdef and itemdef2, put the models in the raw folder in the cache, and all that. I don't know if this is 100% the item thing, but here's the error I get when i try to start my server: [code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ExceptionInInitializerError Caused by: java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 6 at server.world.ItemHandler.loadItemList(ItemHandler.java:377) at server.world.ItemHandler.<init>(ItemHandler.java:34) at server.Server.<clinit>(Server.java:62) Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
